в”Ӯ рҹ“Ұ Hitbox Expansion Risks
в”Ӯ вҖў The Hitbox Expander modifies HumanoidRootPart properties such as:
в”Ӯ   вҖў Size
в”Ӯ   вҖў Transparency
в”Ӯ   вҖў Color
в”Ӯ   вҖў Material
в”Ӯ   вҖў CanCollide
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ вҖў Depending on the game, this may cause:
в”Ӯ   вҖў Desynchronization
в”Ӯ   вҖў Physics instability
в”Ӯ   вҖў Immediate kicks
в”Ӯ   вҖў Integrity check detections
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ вҡ пёҸ NOTE
в”Ӯ вҖў The Hitbox Expander was designed primarily around Zee Hood [MACRO]
в”Ӯ   and may not function consistently in all Roblox experiences.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Games with advanced anti-cheat systems may detect one or more of the
в”Ӯ following behaviors:
в”Ӯ вҖў Direct camera manipulation
в”Ӯ вҖў Synthetic mouse input
в”Ӯ вҖў Overlay rendering
в”Ӯ вҖў Character property modification
в”Ӯ вҖў Repeated raycasting
в”Ӯ вҖў Unusual targeting patterns
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ If a game performs behavioral analysis, detection remains possible.
