в”ңв”Җ рҹ§  RESOLVER OVERVIEW в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ This version includes a built-in Resolver system that substantially
в”Ӯ improves resistance against many common Anti-Lock scripts.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Current resolver features:
в”Ӯ вҖў Position-based velocity reconstruction
в”Ӯ вҖў Velocity smoothing using linear interpolation
в”Ӯ вҖў Maximum velocity clamping
в”Ӯ вҖў Configurable resolver strength
в”Ӯ вҖў Automatic stale-data cleanup
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The prediction system now uses resolved velocity rather than relying
в”Ӯ solely on raw AssemblyLinearVelocity.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       local Resolved_Velocity =
в”Ӯ           Get_Resolved_Velocity(Target, Delta_Time)
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       local Predicted_Position =
в”Ӯ           Target.Position +
в”Ӯ           (Resolved_Velocity * Settings.Prediction)
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ This significantly improves accuracy against:
в”Ӯ вҖў 1пёҸвғЈ Fake Velocity Spoofing
в”Ӯ вҖў 2пёҸвғЈ Sudden Velocity Spikes
в”Ӯ вҖў 3пёҸвғЈ Basic Desync Movement
в”Ӯ вҖў 4пёҸвғЈ Jitter-Based Anti-Lock
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ вҡ пёҸ LIMITATIONS
в”Ӯ вҖў No public resolver can guarantee perfect tracking against all
в”Ӯ   advanced Anti-Lock methods, especially severe CFrame desynchronization
в”Ӯ   or server-side position manipulation.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ вҖў However, this version is dramatically more resilient than the
в”Ӯ   original BETA release.
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җ рҹҡҖ FUTURE IMPROVEMENTS в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Yes вҖ” all of the limitations above can be significantly mitigated.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Examples of advanced improvements include:
в”Ӯ вҖў Velocity sanity checks
в”Ӯ вҖў Desync detection
в”Ӯ вҖў Advanced resolver systems
в”Ӯ вҖў Improved raycast filtering
в”Ӯ вҖў Camera smoothing randomization
в”Ӯ вҖў Secure trigger methods
в”Ӯ вҖў Adaptive anti-lock bypasses
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Implementing these protections is straightforward for experienced
в”Ӯ developers.
в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ However, they are intentionally NOT included in this public BETA
в”Ӯ release.
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җ рҹҡ« WHY THESE FIXES ARE NOT INCLUDED в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
